title: Zach Cregger
description: Yes!! Zach Cregger (Whitest Kids U Know) is just a delightful guest with whom to make it weird. What a weird way to say a simple thing: he's hilarious, thoughtful and thoughtfully hilarious. They get deep, they get weird, dare we say they keep it MFing crispy, y'all!
